;
;I# 645 : Tome Bound with human skin
INUMBER 645
NAME 545
WEIGHT 5
VOLUME 3
IFPREVERB TURN -1
	ECHO PLAYER You find yourself unable to turn the page.
CLEARVERB
ENDIF
TURNABLE
*DESCRIPTION_START EXAMINE
The human skin of the tome has been colored with a black die. Silvery words on the cover read, "THE KEYS TO MAGICAL POWER."
*DESCRIPTION_END
IFPREVERB READ -1
	ECHO OTHERS %N pores over the tome bound with human skin.
	ECHO PLAYER "Trial the first: Thou shalt locate a vial of the ichor known to flow through the veins of a greater daemon of Idemmu Ag. Thou shall prove thy success by pouring this ichor upon this tome. Only then shalt thou have proven thyself worthy to turn the page.
	CLEARVERB
ENDIF
