;I# 1167 : Kvantar warrior (CB)
INUMBER 1167
NAME 958
MISC
WEIGHT 1000
VOLUME 40
HIDDEN
IFPREVERB KICK -1
	ECHO PLAYER You kick the stuffed kvantar warrior and its eyes start flashing with red and green lights.
	ECHO OTHERS %N kicks the stuffed kvantar warrior and its eyes start flashing with red and green lights.
	CLEARVERB
ENDIF
IFPREVERB THUMP -1
	ECHO PLAYER You thump on the kvantar warrior and it emits a low growl.
	ECHO OTHERS %N thumps on the kvantar warrior and it emits a low growl.
	CLEARVERB
ENDIF
IFPREVERB POKE -1
	ECHO PLAYER When you poke the kvantar warrior, it turns its head in your direction.
	ECHO OTHERS When %N pokes the kvantar warrior, it turns its head in %h direction.
	CLEARVERB
ENDIF
IFPREVERB WINK -1
	ECHO PLAYER The kvantar warrior winks back at you.
	ECHO OTHERS %N and the kvantar warrior exchange winks.
	CLEARVERB
ENDIF
