NAME 441
WEIGHT 4
VOLUME 5
PARAMETER1 3
PUNCTURE_WEAPON
CRAFTABLE
ENCRUSTABLE
SUBSTANCE HARDMETAL
IFPREVERB PULL -1
          IFITEM -1 WIELDED
                 CLEARVERB
                 ECHO PLAYER You raise %a in salute.
