;
; Saliva for crimson
INUMBER 1514
NAME 1046
WEIGHT 1
VOLUME 1
LIGHTABLE
DYE
REAGENT
PARAMETER1 1
PARAMETER3 75
ARTICLE SOME
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM
The now cooled saliva is a bit like red clay with tiny flecks of amber imbedded in it.
*DESCRIPTION_END
IFPREVERB LIGHT -1
	IFVAR QUESTISON = 0
		CLEARVERB
		REMOVEITEM -1
		ECHO OTHERS As %n brings a flame near the saliva, it begins to smolder....
		ECHO OTHERS As You bring a flame near the saliva, it begins to smolder....
		RANDOM DUMMY3 1 3 0
		IFVAR DUMMY3 = 3
			DAMAGEALL BURN 50 The saliva explodes into a huge fire ball surrounding you with flames!
		ENDIF
		IFVAR DUMMY3 = 2
			DAMAGEALL BURN 50 The saliva explodes into a huge fire ball surrounding you with flames!
			KILL PLAYER
			POSITION LAY
			ECHO PLAYER You are blown to bits!
		ENDIF
		IFVAR DUMMY3 = 1
			ECHO OTHERS The saliva explodes into a huge fire ball that engulfs %N!
			KILL PLAYER
			POSITION LAY
			ECHO PLAYER You are blown to bits!
		ENDIF
	ENDIF
	IFVAR QUESTISON ! 0
		ECHO PLAYER Lighting off beetle saliva during a quest would not be regarded as fair play.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFVERB CONCENTRATE -1
	IFVAR SKILL20 > 0
		LIGHT -1
		ECHO ALL The %a begins to glow a bit, making a nice little light source for %n.
	ENDIF
	IFVAR SKILL20 = 0
		DAMAGEPLR BODYONLY 10 It hurts to think that hard with an untrained mind.
	ENDIF
ENDIF
