;

VARIABLE PATHUNTER
; Horn
INUMBER 519
NAME 458
SKIN
WEIGHT 1
VOLUME 1
SUBSTANCE INDESTRUCTABLE
IFPREVERB LOOK -1
        IFVAR INTNUM3 = 1
        CLEARVERB
        ECHO PLAYER Gradrak says, " This item is a skinitem horn if there are no itembits and a hunter's horn if ITEMBIT0 = 1.
        ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB PLAY -1
        IFVAR ITEMBIT0 = 1
                clearverb
                IFVAR PATHUNTER = 1
                ECHO PLAYER You take a deep breath and blow into the horn. You sound a majestic note.
                ECHO OTHERS %N raises %h horn to %h lips and breaks the silence by sounding a majestic note.
                GMMSG **%N blew the hunter's horn!**
                ECHO ALL The note hangs in the air and seems to take on a life of its own. You can hear the mournful call echo back and forth.
                ECHO ALL Finally, the echoing note begins to die out, but just as it does, you notice a patch of darkness coalesce nearby.
                ELSE
                ECHO PLAYER You take a deep breath and blow into the horn. You sound a majestic note.
                ECHO OTHERS %N raises %h horn to %h lips and breaks the silence by sounding a majestic note.
        ENDIF
ENDIF
