*DESCRIPTION_START READ
+----------------------------------------------------------------+
|               Tarinth's Eternity Incorporated                  |
|                   Death Insurance Policy                       |
|               "We're there beacause we care."                  |
|                                                                |
| Eternity Death Insurance Incorporated agrees, in the event of  |
| the INSURED's death, to locate them in an area of one hundred  |
| leagues radius from the city of Fayd*, and restore them to life |
| in circumstances including but not necessarily limited to      |
| death due to accident, fire, earthquaqe, war, lightning strike |
| or other act of deity, murder, monster, trap and misadventure. |
|                                                                |
| Under no circumstances will Eternity Death Insurance, Inc.,    |
| its agents, executives or employees be liable for loss of      |
| posessions or detriment to post-resurrection health however,   |
| Eternity Death Insurance shall make the best attempt possible  |
| to restore the INSURED to a state similar to that previous of  |
| death. Eternity Death Insurance Inc. will under not interfere  |
| with the legal process of justice in the city of Fayd insofar  |
| as just and lawful death penalties are imposed.                |
| * We no longer serve the Deep Realms.                          |
+----------------------------------------------------------------+
*DESCRIPTION_END
